body:
# Code participation

[Launchpad page](https://launchpad.net/~yatc18ks0g8zofezrpk-me)

## Gwibber
_Micro-blogging client for Linux_

Maintenance does not clean links (12/08/2012) [Bug report + patch](https://bugs.launchpad.net/gwibber/+bug/1035962)

Pasted URL always shortened even when turned off (25/03/2012) [Patch](https://bugs.launchpad.net/gwibber/+bug/896639)

## Mustard
_Micro-blogging client for Android_

Does not store the OAuth keys in a secured way (16/08/12) [Bug report](https://bugs.launchpad.net/mustardroid/+bug/1037760)

## Request-oauth
_Python library for making OAuth requests_

Created [python 3 port](https://github.com/maraujop/requests-oauth/issues/21) (19/05/2012)

Import error in tests function (28/04/2012) [Patch](https://github.com/maraujop/requests-oauth/commit/252aec309b2f5a62cb50fcf349a61b156d46e8b7)


# Other
